{"tid":1847802,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"全城抗炎！無綫要員工量體溫　湖北返港要隔離","createTime":"2020-01-28T08:13:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T08:22:20.000Z","uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"44a3e2d1b626984c7faf4d403f636f7d72c008a4","tid":1847802,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T08:13:01.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情的擴散趨勢仍然未止，政府今日宣布明日（29日）起實施特別上班安排，除提供緊急和必須公共服務的人員外，政府僱員在假期後毋須返回寫字樓辦公，改為家中工作。因應病疫情況，無綫亦向員工今日發出通告，指由明日起所有職、藝員進入電視城前，均需要量度體溫，如發現有發燒者，會被勸籲回家休息。而如有同事由湖北返港，不論係因公幹或旅遊，均需自行在家隔離14日，並作有薪病假處理。而傳媒進入電視廣播城時，亦需要配合相關處理措施。<br />\n<br />\n另外，有線寬頻亦宣布在明日（29日）起至下周一（2月2日）將會實施抗疫措施：「1.身體不適及懷孕員工毋須上班工作。2.因應工作需要而回辦公室輪班工作之員工，工作時間將作彈性安排，呼籲員工避免於繁忙時間使用公共運輸交通。3.各後勤部門員工因應部門主管安排及工作需要可在家工作。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200128/photo/bkn-20200128130809183-0128_00862_001_02p.jpg?20200128155937\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200128%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200128130809183-0128_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20200128155937&h=7ee95f96&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b832e4cb9f8413189804fed6a9a53d053585472c","tid":1847802,"uid":317233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T08:13:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>熱烈欢迎全国同胞來港免费就医！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1847735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1847735</a></strong></span>"},{"pid":"96699acc5b3e514d3de12a026a5228a646216188","tid":1847802,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T08:16:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c762a6a9d8baa98490bd837c68b3078ca04760be","tid":1847802,"uid":303052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T08:22:20.000Z","msg":"唔好意思樓主借個位俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫我spread文宣出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />ig同Facebook都要見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">香港人與醫護同行</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/njWo9TN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnjWo9TN.png&h=5749623d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f2CvPTP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff2CvPTP.png&h=a9ffb879&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}